::Feline::

She stepped out of hte chamber and saw Firearm there.  She walked 
over to him, with her body swaying and smiling at him.  She stopped 
righ next to him, "I just wanted to thank you again."  She leaned 
over and kissed him again on the cheek.  She leaned back and smiled.  
She spoke in a soft, breathy voice,"I'm Feline. I didn't catch your 
name handsome?"
She stood there with one hand on her hip and her tail swaying behind 
her.
